{"id":7531,"date":"2021-10-10T20:48:02","date_gmt":"2021-10-10T13:48:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=7531"},"modified":"2023-11-22T12:46:41","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T05:46:41","slug":"shophouse-la-gi-co-nen-dau-tu-vao-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/shophouse-la-gi-co-nen-dau-tu-vao-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kinh doanh h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c <strong>Shophouse<\/strong> \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00ednh kh\u1ea3 d\u1ee5ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u0103n nh\u00e0 theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00e0m khu gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, mua s\u1eafm v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> s\u1ebd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Shophouse la\u0300 gi\u0300? \u01afu \u2013 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o n\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7544\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7544\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7544 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"437\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/437;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7544\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7544\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"437\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7544\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>Vinhomes Grand Park Qu\u1eadn 9<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shophouse la\u0300 gi\u0300?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Con ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m Shophouse t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 50 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 XIX. Shophouse c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0: c\u0103n h\u1ed9 kinh doanh hay nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i,\u2026V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, shophouse ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9, nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eeba l\u00e0m nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u1eeba l\u00e0m n\u01a1i kinh doanh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, shophouse s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t d\u00e3y ph\u1ed1 kinh doanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7545\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7545\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7545 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-nha-pho-thuong-mai.jpg\" alt=\"Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i (Shophouse)\" width=\"800\" height=\"402\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/402;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7545\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7545\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-nha-pho-thuong-mai.jpg\" alt=\"Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i (Shophouse)\" width=\"800\" height=\"402\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7545\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i (Shophouse)<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c kinh doanh shophouse kh\u00e1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng v\u1eady. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S \u0111\u1ec1u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng khu t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng shophouse v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0ng nh\u1eb1m thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">U\u031bu \u0111ie\u0302\u0309m nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i shophouse \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c N\u0110T. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c, m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh Shophouse. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9\/nh\u00e0 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf t\u1ea7ng tr\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u00f2a chung c\u01b0, trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S,\u2026 nh\u1eb1m mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 thu h\u00fat kinh doanh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, N\u0110T c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kinh doanh ho\u1eb7c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7538 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/kinh-nghiem-mua-shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"507\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/507;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7538\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/kinh-nghiem-mua-shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"507\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i shophouse, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i di chuy\u1ec3n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch. B\u1edfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110T nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t shop house.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng cao<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh shophouse ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 nhu c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c nhau: c\u01b0 tr\u00fa v\u00e0 kinh doanh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho N\u0110T c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u cho chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e2ng cao l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn khi kinh doanh.\u00a0<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mua \u0111i b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u0103n shophouse th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1c c\u0103n shophouse l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf t\u00ednh thanh kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u0103n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. N\u0110T B\u0110S c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111i b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c cho thu\u00ea.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7532 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/1-shophouse-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/419;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7532\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/1-shophouse-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhu\u031bo\u031b\u0323c \u0111ie\u0302\u0309m shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u00ean, shophouse c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd. N\u0110T c\u1ea7n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Shophouse ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean l\u01b0u \u00fd<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh cao h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong khu k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 kinh doanh, nh\u1eefng c\u0103n shophouse th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u0103n h\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u1ee5c tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 shophouse th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00edt \u1ecfi. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f4i khi N\u0110T c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh ho\u1eb7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m cho gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u0103n shophouse ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u0103ng cao.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7541 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7541\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kinh doanh shophouse kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 kinh doanh m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh shophouse kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho N\u0110T hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. B\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u01b0 d\u00e2n trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh kinh doanh shophouse v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn shophouse \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a d\u00e2n c\u01b0 c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ai. T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh , nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thu\u00ea\/ mua shophouse v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kinh doanh.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, shophouse s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u N\u0110T lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong kho\u1ea3ng 50 n\u0103m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a N\u0110T khi mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0103n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch d\u00e0nh cho shophouse m\u1edbi sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7540\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7540\" class=\"wp-image-7540 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/phap-ly-shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian\" width=\"800\" height=\"620\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/620;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7540\" class=\"wp-image-7540 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/phap-ly-shophouse-1.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian\" width=\"800\" height=\"620\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7540\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>Grand Marina Saigon Qu\u1eadn 1<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha\u0301p ly\u0301 ca\u0302\u0300n bie\u0302\u0301t ve\u0302\u0300 shophouse<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u1ec1 shophouse nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf l\u00e0 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf quy ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ebf c\u00e1c t\u00f2a chung c\u01b0, th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng 1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7ng 5, c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\/kinh doanh trong v\u00f2ng 50 n\u0103m. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, N\u0110T c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhu c\u1ea7u kinh doanh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 50 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y mua, c\u0103n shophouse s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c N\u0110T ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i cho C\u0110T.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7547\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7547\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7547 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-vinhomes-central-park.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"448\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/448;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7547\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7547\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-vinhomes-central-park.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"448\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7547\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf chung c\u01b0<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eb1m nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf. V\u00ec v\u1eady N\u0110T s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd nh\u01b0: t\u1ea1m v\u1eafng hay t\u1ea1m tr\u00fa,\u2026 B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shophouse th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 theo quy ho\u1ea1ch C\u0110T \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy\u1ec7t. C\u0103n h\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh theo \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 lu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u0103n shophouse kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf thi\u1ebfu.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7550\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7550\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7550 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/uu-diem-cua-nha-pho-thuong-mai-la-gi-1-1024x576-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7550\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7550\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/uu-diem-cua-nha-pho-thuong-mai-la-gi-1-1024x576-1.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7550\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shophouse th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n shophouse, N\u0110T c\u1ea7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0: quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n v\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng shophouse, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng shophouse, chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, th\u1eddi gian giao nh\u1eadn,\u2026N\u1ebfu trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t tranh ch\u1ea5p, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn khi mua b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c thu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 x\u1eed l\u00fd.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Co\u0301 ne\u0302n mua shophouse hay kh\u00f4ng?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y, shophouse s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c B\u0110S n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua\/kinh doanh shophouse ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, N\u0110T s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch \u0111a d\u1ea1ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft Co\u0301 ne\u0302n mua shophouse hay kh\u00f4ng r\u1ed3i<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u00fa \u00fd r\u1eb1ng, ph\u00e1p l\u00fd cho shophouse \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c N\u0110T g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7546 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-van-canh.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/600;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7546\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/shophouse-van-canh.jpg\" alt=\"Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t, N\u0110T c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kinh doanh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\"><strong>vinhomeland.com.vn<\/strong><\/a>, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1<strong> shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/strong> c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a shophouse. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;7531&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Shophouse l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? C\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o shophouse kh\u00f4ng?&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-r